StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetProfessedNonMepsExam]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@ProspectID uniqueiden..er = null, @ExamID uniqueiden..er = null
AS BEGIN
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED SET NOCOUNT ON
SELECT p.ID ,p.ProspectID ,p.ExamType ,p.ExamDate ,p.ExamEnteredDate ,p.Score ,p.PiCatMmScore ,p.PiCatGtScore ,p.PiCatElScore ,p.PiCatClScore ,p.CareerDecision ,e.PROFESSED_EXAM_SHORT_DESC AS ExamDesc FROM USMC.ProspectNonMEPSProfessedExam p JOIN MCRISS.dbo.PROFESSED_EXAM e ON p.ExamType = e.PROFESSED_EXAM_TYPE WHERE (@ProspectID IS NULL OR ProspectID = @ProspectID) AND (@ExamID IS NULL OR ID = @ExamID) ORDER BY ExamDate Desc END
